		// ========== DIVINIY ==========

		// === Earpiece:

		// INTRO:
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Intro01" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">(No sound) Look! You save it as an emergency and watch the AI ​​machine destroy the building. This is where the offices of Aperture Eastern-7 and Aperture North America are located."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Intro02" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">This joke should not be missed… because not long?"
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Intro03" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">This place is amazing. You have to get up in the morning, but... the book. Relationships and so on. I think the only way is to try. I hope you will update this page. This is the easy part, so if you're an expert, you're good to go."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Intro04" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">You must do it! They should be in the next room... maybe next to each other. stay at home"
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Intro05" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">And... channels. I want our house to be beautiful."

		// CHAMBER:
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_PinkPlate" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">You will be surprised! This is the last camera on the list and we've moved on to the fun stuff."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_Traversal" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">You know it's a red dress. It's unacceptable, it's a shame and I love it."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_WallBlocksWall" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">This is a beautiful home! The place has been vacant for years. I hope to start soon."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_FieldIntro" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">And what is development? What happened to this place? continues"
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_FunnelTower" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">Unfortunately, resources are limited. That's one of the reasons we do it."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Chamber_Transit" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">Oh...autumn is worse than summer! Vegetables grow everywhere. The leaves are damaged. I wish all the trees in the world were green."

		// CORE01:
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Core01_01" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">There are many ways."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Core01_02" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">...I think this is a story that happens to all of us. I will take a look at the damage when I get back and see what needs to be fixed."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Core01_03" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">I know it's not easy to improve if you prove your skills in these areas. A few specific functions are needed, but unfortunately they are scattered and little known."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Core01_04" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">That was the first. I think the media gives a negative impression that we are inferior to others."

		// SOFTLOCKS:
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Softlock_01" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">Hmm... just... he had no appetite or hunger. I understand, but what happens when an accident occurs? This is great…"
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Softlock_02" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">So smart people like you are good at math? I hope I'm wrong."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Softlock_03" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">Yes, all features are unlocked. Do yourself a favor."
		"Divinity_Earpiece.VO_Softlock_04" = "<font color=\"rgb(78,158,255)\">No more links...so come back here after you die. So everything will be fine, thanks"



		// === Easter eggs:

		"Divinity_EasterEgg.VO_Shrine_Grrahhhhh" = "<font color=\"rgb(132,0,255)\">Hello, my name is Sokona Lemon! ! ! God! ! Title: Wrong! ! !"
	}
